descript.abstract: This data set consists of all trust parcels on State Trust land. The data are created to serve as base information for use in GIS systems for a variety of planning and analysis purposes. Access is granted to public agencies, educational institutions, non-profit organizations and private individuals for non-commercial purpose. For commercial use of the data see Arizona Revised Statutes 39-121.03. All monthly updates to the surface parcels are performed by the ASLD's GIS Department through a series of editing procedures. 11/2022
